  <summary date="2022-11-03T17:25:26Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Hydrogen Infrastructure Finance and Innovation Act

This bill requires the Department of Energy (DOE) to establish a hydrogen infrastructure finance and innovation pilot program. Under the program, DOE must provide grants and low-interest loans to certain entities for hydrogen infrastructure, including projects for hydrogen transportation, storage, or delivery.</summary>
